To reach the final quotient rule structure, we find a common denominator of $(v(x))^2$:

$$
\begin{aligned}
f'(x) &= \frac{u'(x)v(x)}{(v(x))^2} - \frac{u(x)v'(x)}{(v(x))^2} \\
&= \frac{v(x)u'(x) - u(x)v'(x)}{(v(x))^2}
\end{aligned}
$$

This algebraic form satisfies the **quotient rule structure** required by the markscheme.
